Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//--------------------OPJP 1--------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.64,0:00:14.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}もう散々ぐるぐるしたじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:16.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}やるときやらなきゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:21.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}いままでのダイナミックだって　ダイナシだよ！？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.57,0:00:24.24,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\move(640,12.5,638,-5.5,9,551)}精いっぱい純情かさねて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ほらほら　チェックメイト！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:28.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}...って言うところで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:31.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}キミは一歩踏んで　百歩下がる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:34.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}素晴らしいコトバを授けよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:36.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}can't guess the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:39.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}"その目をしたキミに不可能などはない！"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:41.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}say never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:43.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}カラフルボードゲームは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:46.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}本日も波瀾万丈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:51.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}天使の弓　不敵な笑み　嵐が始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:56.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}流星回転　ルーレット　Rally Go Round
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:57.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}you are the player
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:01:01.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ハート形の矢印で貫こう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:02.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}you are my love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:07.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}いま最強最大LOVEを込めた手のひらで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.45,0:01:11.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}背中叩くから　ありったけかっとばせ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:12.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}don't miss your big chance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:15.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}諸君のカクゴに見合う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:17.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}良い知らせ　待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:19.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}新記録の心拍数
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:23.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}乗り越え　見せてみてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:25.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}...ってば　ちゃんと聞いてんの？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//--------------------OPCN 1--------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.64,0:00:14.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你看這不都已經搞的一團亂了？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.18,0:00:16.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}該做的時候就該出手！
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.20,0:00:21.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}努力到現在的所有衝勁　全都白費了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.57,0:00:24.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}盡全力揮灑的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你瞧　就在要快要說出『將軍』！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:28.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}的這個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:31.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}而你踏出了一步　卻又離你更遠了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.33,0:00:34.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}那就告訴你一個美妙的話語吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:36.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}can't guess the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:39.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}「在妳的視線裡　沒有什麼是不可能的！」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:41.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}say never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:43.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在這變化多端的棋盤遊戲裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:46.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}今天也是波瀾萬丈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:51.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}天使的武器就是那無懼的笑容　風暴即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:56.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}流星迴轉　輪盤　開始轉起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:57.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}you are the player
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:01:01.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}射出心型的飛鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:02.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}you are my love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:07.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}將至今最強最大的愛灌注到瞄準的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.45,0:01:11.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我會將你投出　請盡全力飛翔吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:12.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}don't miss your big chance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:15.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}各位的覺悟中
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.75,0:01:17.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}都等待著看到好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:19.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}那就超越心跳的新紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:23.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}給我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:25.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}喂　我說你有聽進去吧？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//--------------------EDJP 1--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:26.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}飛び交ったキミ電波網をくぐり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:31.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}背伸びでキャッチした想いは空振りだ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.28,0:12:37.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}発信源を見つけ次第早急に
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.58,0:12:42.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}ぶつけようあれこれ気がすむまで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:45.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}容量がいっばいで
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.55,0:12:48.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}処理できないけど
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}熱の正体は
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.76,0:12:53.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}スキ？　スキ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:56.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}っぽい感情
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}かな？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.56,0:13:00.35,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}迷い道寄って
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.35,0:13:03.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}距離感を知って
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.15,0:13:08.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}今の私は恋の色も夢も全部
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.86,0:13:14.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}わからないいまま手探りのまま
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.62,0:13:19.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}慌しい日々　胸を押さえて行こう
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}内緒で送った　本音のメッセージ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.67,0:13:26.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}開らく鍵は　届いた？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//--------------------EDCN 1--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:26.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}飛進了　屬於你的電波領域
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:31.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}伸出手來　想捕捉訊號　卻撲了個空
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.28,0:12:37.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一找到發信源就立刻連上
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.58,0:12:42.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}傳送著自己的心情　直到滿足為止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:45.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}容量太過龐大
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.55,0:12:48.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}無法立即處理
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}過熱的原因是
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.76,0:12:53.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}喜歡？　喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:56.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}好像是喜歡的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}感情？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.56,0:13:00.35,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}藉由迷惘的感覺　
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.35,0:13:03.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}摸清了彼此的距離感
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.15,0:13:08.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}現在的我　心中全部都是戀愛的色彩還有夢想
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.86,0:13:14.33,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}因為從未經歷過　所以一點一點地摸索
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.62,0:13:19.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}繁忙的日子　壓抑著心中的衝動
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}秘密地發送　真心的訊息
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.67,0:13:26.05,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}開啟的鑰匙　傳達到了嗎？
